---
import { Plus, Minus } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Get answers to common questions about HVAC system design and our professional engineering services
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Items -->
    <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-6 sm:p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-6 sm:pr-8">
              What information do you need to design an HVAC system?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-5 sm:w-6 h-5 sm:h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-8 pb-6 sm:pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
            We need building plans, occupancy schedules, local climate data, intended use of spaces, 
            and any specific comfort or air quality requirements. Our team will also conduct a site visit 
            to assess existing conditions and constraints for optimal system design.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-6 sm:p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-6 sm:pr-8">
              How do you ensure energy efficiency in HVAC design?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-5 sm:w-6 h-5 sm:h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-8 pb-6 sm:pb-8">
          <div class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-2 sm:space-y-3 text-sm sm:text-base">
            <p>Our energy-efficient designs include proper load calculations, high-efficiency equipment selection, 
            optimized ductwork design, and advanced control strategies including variable speed drives and smart thermostats.</p>
            <p>We also incorporate energy recovery systems, zoning controls, and building automation 
            to minimize energy consumption while maintaining optimal comfort levels.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-6 sm:p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-6 sm:pr-8">
              What HVAC design standards and codes do you follow?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-5 sm:w-6 h-5 sm:h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-8 pb-6 sm:pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
            We follow ASHRAE standards including 90.1 for energy efficiency, Manual J/S/D for load calculations, 
            and all applicable local mechanical codes (IMC/UMC). Our designs also comply with NFPA safety standards 
            and local building code amendments to ensure full regulatory compliance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-6 sm:p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-6 sm:pr-8">
              How long does the HVAC design process typically take?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-5 sm:w-6 h-5 sm:h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-8 pb-6 sm:pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
            Typical residential projects take 2-3 weeks, while commercial projects require 6-8 weeks depending 
            on complexity. The process includes load calculations (1-2 weeks), system design (2-3 weeks), 
            CAD development (2-3 weeks), and final review (1 week) with regular client updates throughout.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-6 sm:p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-6 sm:pr-8">
              Can you design HVAC systems for existing buildings?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-5 sm:w-6 h-5 sm:h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-8 pb-6 sm:pb-8">
          <div class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-2 sm:space-y-3 text-sm sm:text-base">
            <p>Yes, we specialize in retrofit and renovation projects. We assess existing infrastructure, 
            ductwork, and electrical systems to design optimal solutions that work within existing constraints.</p>
            <p>Our retrofit designs often include upgrades to improve efficiency, indoor air quality, 
            and comfort while minimizing disruption to building occupants during installation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-6 sm:p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-6 sm:pr-8">
              Do you provide installation support and commissioning services?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-5 sm:w-6 h-5 sm:h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-8 pb-6 sm:pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
            We provide comprehensive installation support including contractor coordination, site visits 
            during installation, system startup assistance, and commissioning services to ensure optimal 
            performance. Our team remains available throughout the project lifecycle for technical support.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left p-6 sm:p-8 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:bg-gray-50">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 pr-6 sm:pr-8">
              What CAD formats and deliverables do you provide?
            </h3>
            <Plus className="w-5 sm:w-6 h-5 sm:h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" />
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-8 pb-6 sm:pb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
            We deliver complete design packages including AutoCAD (.dwg) and Revit MEP (.rvt) files, 
            PDF construction documents, equipment schedules, load calculation reports, and 3D BIM models. 
            All drawings follow AIA/NCS standards for seamless integration with project teams.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12 sm:mt-16">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-cyan-500 text-white p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 sm:mb-4">Ready to Design Your HVAC System?</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-100 mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-sm sm:text-base">Our HVAC engineers are ready to create efficient, comfortable solutions for your project</p>
        <a href="/contact?#contact-form" class="bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-300 inline-block text-sm sm:text-base">
          Start Your Project
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  // Add FAQ toggle functionality
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const faqButtons = document.querySelectorAll('section button');
    
    faqButtons.forEach(button => {
      button.addEventListener('click', function(this: HTMLButtonElement) {
        const content = this.nextElementSibling as HTMLElement;
        const icon = this.querySelector('svg');
        
        if (content.style.display === 'none' || content.style.display === '') {
          content.style.display = 'block';
          icon?.classList.remove('lucide-plus');
          icon?.classList.add('lucide-minus');
        } else {
          content.style.display = 'none';
          icon?.classList.remove('lucide-minus');
          icon?.classList.add('lucide-plus');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>